title: Simple Bow Flat Shoes
description:
Ultimate Staple

  • Faux PU leather
  • Removable ankle strap
  • Adjustable heart buckled cross foot straps
  • Low heel: approx .5in

This item is made by Sosic Shop in China. It ships directly from the vendor. Please allow eight to ten weeks for international delivery.
